# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  CV Project — .gitignore
#  Strategy: ignore everything by default, whitelist safe types
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Ignore everything by default
*

# ── Un-ignore safe tracked types ──────────────────────────────
!*/
!*.tex
!*.md
!*.sh
!*.zsh
!*.py
!*.js
!*.mjs
!*.svg
!*.jpg
!.env.example
!.gitignore
!master_cv.example.json
# uv project files — required for reproducible `uv sync` installs
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock

# ── Secrets and credentials — NEVER commit ────────────────────
.env
.linkedin_token.json
*.token.json
*.credentials.json

# ── Project instructions — personal data inside ───────────────
CLAUDE.md

# ── Personal CV data — keep private ───────────────────────────
master_cv.json
master_cv*.json
!master_cv.example.json

# ── Actual personal data files (real name/email/phone inside) ─
templates/shared/personal_data.tex
templates/shared/personal_data.json

# ── LaTeX class files — safe to track ─────────────────────────
!*.cls

# ── Old/legacy template folders — have hardcoded personal data ─
templates/experimental/

# ── Job applications — private (names, letters, rejections) ───
Applied/
recommendation_letter/

# ── Specific applications with personal name / company info ───
cover_letters/CoverLetter_*.tex
cover_letters/lettre_*.tex
cover_letters/review/

# ── LinkedIn content — post ideas and strategies are private ──
linkedin/idees_posts.md

# ── LinkedIn profile rebuild & career roadmap — personal data ──
LINKEDIN_REBUILD.md
NETDEVOPS_ROADMAP.md

# ── One-off / throwaway scripts & scraped data — private, not part of the app ──
scripts/oneoff/

# ── IDE / editor configs ──────────────────────────────────────
.cursor/

# ── Data folder — personal cache and profile data ─────────────
data/

# ── Generated output files ────────────────────────────────────
output/
templates/lato/output/
templates/*/output/
*.pdf
*.txt

# ── LaTeX build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────
*.aux
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.log
*.out
*.synctex.gz
*.bbl
*.blg

# ── Python environment ────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# ── Runtime and temp ──────────────────────────────────────────
log/
*.tmp
scratch*.py
test_*.tex
test_*.py
*_mock.py
run_mock.py
*_draft.*
tmp_*.py

# ── Binaries and media ────────────────────────────────────────
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.gz
*.zip

# ── macOS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store

# Whitelist project logo assets
!assets/project_logo.jpg
!assets/linkedin_su6i.svg

# ── Personal session logs & task lists — NEVER track (privacy) ──
SESSION.md
TODO.md

# ── Roles registry — safe to track (NO personal data; needed at runtime) ──
# ONLY this specific file is whitelisted. Any OTHER file under config/ stays
# ignored, so personal data accidentally written to a new config file is NOT
# committed. NEVER put names / emails / phones / local paths in roles.yaml —
# personal data belongs only in templates/shared/personal_data.* (gitignored).
!config/roles.yaml

# ── Registry contract tests (override the test_*.py ignore above) ──
!tests/test_roles.py
